@startuml
title State: Trip lifecycle

[*] --> Planned
Planned --> Booked : transport+accommodation booked
Booked --> Prepared : documents+packing ready
Prepared --> Traveling : departure
Traveling --> AtDestination : arrival
AtDestination --> Traveling : day trips / transfers
AtDestination --> Completed : return home
Traveling --> Completed : arrived home
Completed --> [*]

Booked --> Canceled : cancel booking
Planned --> Canceled : cancel idea
Canceled --> [*]
@enduml
